high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the glass from behind the sharp knife.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the glass down in the sink, clean the glass with water, pick up the glass.
Turn around and walk to the wooden shelves to the left of the counter.
Put the glass down on the right side of the second shelf.
anns.task_desc: To clean a glass and put it on the shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the glass off of the counter.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the sink.
Put the glass in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean glass from the sink.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn right to face the wooden shelving unit to the left of the counter.
Put the clean glass on the right side of the middle shelf of the wooden shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean glass on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn right walk 4 steps then turn left towards the counter.
Pick up the glass from the counter.
Turn around take one step then turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the glass in the sink, turn on the tap and fill the glass with water then pick up the filled glass.
Turn around walk to the end of the room then turn right towards the cabinet.
Place the glass on the lower shelf of the cabinet beside the existing glass.
anns.task_desc: Fill the glass with water and put it in the cabinet.
